rComments: Awesome teacher. Easy A if you attend classes and study.

There is no textbook in this class (PSY3123), so you have to attend all the lectures. The tests are a combination of multiple-choice and short-essay questions. He is a very tough grader. The lectures are incredibly boring and unless you're a great notetaker, you will not pass this class. Would not recommend.

Had him in PSY3508 and PSY3536, he is a very good teacher. He makes lectures interesting and makes sure his exames reflect understanding and not only learning by heart. He is also very open to discussion for you awnsers... I would recommend 100%

Very easy A if you read the book - all you need to do is read the assigned chapters and write down the definitions provided in orange once and you're basically guaranteed 90% or higher. Not an extraordinary teacher, but clearly explains the material and what's expected of you. Multiple choice exams as well, so very easy!

J'ai beaucoup aimé son cours! C'est certain que la matière est difficile et qu'il y a beaucoup à apprendre, mais c'est car c'est un cours de psychologie pareil pour tout le monde. Je trouve qu'il rend la matière intéressante et prend bien le temps de tout expliquer et de ne pas passer au travers toute la matière trop rapidement!Un bon prof a avoir!

This prof does nothing but read from the power points. His multiple choice exams are so hard and he expects you to memorize 100 pages out of the psych book in order to get a good grade on the midterms.
J'ai aimé ce prof. Il ne couvre pas trop de matière parce qu'il prend le temps de vraiment bien l'expliquer et donné beaucoup d'exemples.
In general he's a good professor. Take the time to study and you will pass the class with a good grade !
Awesome class. His lectures are very stimulating and interesting. His exams are easy if you study. His exams are cumulative. Would recommend to anyone.
